iroh-ble-transport — vendored, modified copy
============================================

This directory contains a vendored copy of `iroh-ble-transport`, an
experimental Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) transport for the iroh peer-to-peer
networking stack.

Upstream project : https://github.com/mcginty/iroh-ble-transport
Upstream version : v0.3.1 (git tag `iroh-ble-transport-v0.3.1`)
Original author  : Jake McGinty <me@jakebot.org>
